WEBVTT

00:07:33.520 --> 00:07:34.736
Job training,

00:07:34.760 --> 00:07:35.976
mentoring,

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:37.696
counseling ...

00:07:37.720 --> 00:07:40.456
Teaching young people
to learn from their mistakes

00:07:40.480 --> 00:07:42.176
instead of criminalizing them,

00:07:42.200 --> 00:07:45.720
and dragging them out
of their classrooms like animals.

00:07:47.400 --> 00:07:48.616
How about this?

00:07:48.640 --> 00:07:54.376
I propose that we implement restorative
justice in every high school in America.

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:57.080
(Applause)